   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Step 4: Price and Size Converter Functions\n\nZameen.com displays prices as strings like '1.5 Crore' and sizes like '8 Marla'. These helpers convert them to numeric values (PKR and sqft) for analysis."
   ],
   "id": "5d2b105ef52a58b"
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2026-05-23T07:23:08.863974Z",
     "start_time": "2026-05-23T07:23:08.851921Z"
    }
   },
   "source": [
    "def convert_price(price_str):\n    if not price_str:\n        return None\n    p = price_str.strip()\n    try:\n        if p.endswith(\"Crore\"):    return round(float(p[:-5].strip()) * 10_000_000)\n        if p.endswith(\"Lakh\"):     return round(float(p[:-4].strip()) * 100_000)\n        if p.endswith(\"Million\"):  return round(float(p[:-7].strip()) * 1_000_000)\n        if p.endswith(\"Arab\"):     return round(float(p[:-4].strip()) * 1_000_000_000)\n        if p.endswith(\"Thousand\"): return round(float(p[:-8].strip()) * 1_000)\n        return round(float(p))\n    except:\n        return None\n\ndef convert_size(size_str):\n    if not size_str:\n        return None\n    s = size_str.strip().replace(\",\", \"\")\n    try:\n        if \"Kanal\" in s:   return round(float(re.sub(r'[^0-9.]', '', s)) * 4500)\n        if \"Marla\" in s:   return round(float(re.sub(r'[^0-9.]', '', s)) * 225)\n        if \"Sq. Yd.\" in s: return round(float(re.sub(r'[^0-9.]', '', s)) * 9)\n        if \"Sq. Ft.\" in s: return round(float(re.sub(r'[^0-9.]', '', s)))\n        return round(float(re.sub(r'[^0-9.]', '', s)))\n    except:\n        return None\n\nprint(\"Converter functions ready.\")"
   ],
   "id": "aa2099eaa31b7792",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Converter functions ready.\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "execution_count": 3
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
